    "The reliability formula for a k-out-of-n structure is expressed as R kon (k, n, R) = n r=k n r R r (1 -R) n-r. Building upon this foundation and under the assumption that all components are homogeneous, possessing a reliability function as depicted in 10, and setting n = 6, the potential scenarios can be viewed in figure 16.",
